Jira actually is shipped with a old version of svnkit which is not supporting SASL authentication. Connection to subversion servers 1.5+ is not possible without upgrading to svnkit 1-3-2.

Shipped Jira version should be rolled out with svnkit-1-3-2.

Please see also [JSP-52326|https://support.atlassian.com/browse/JSP-52326]

picking a date for 'created before' or 'created after' _includes_ the specified date in the search.
the resulting search query is
{{created >= 2009-05-25 AND created <= 2009-06-01}}

