It is difficult to set up filter subscriptions to reflect monthly, quarterly, or other periodic data given the limitation of using only >, >=, <, and <= operators. 

Offering functions like SQL's MONTH( ), DAY( ), QUARTER() and YEAR( ) would provide this capability.

